import React from 'react'
import { Decoration,Loginfo,Container,Fullscreen,Imacos} from './LoginElements'
import logo from '../Images/EBlogo.png'

const Login = () => {

  return (
  <Fullscreen>
<Container>
        <Loginfo>
            <Imacos src={logo}/>
        </Loginfo>
        
        <Decoration>
        </Decoration>
    </Container>
  </Fullscreen>
    
  
  )
}

export default Login
